<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>US States API</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; }
        h1 { color: #1e40af; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .endpoint { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 1rem 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h2 { color: #334155; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        code { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 6px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; color: #dc2626; }
        ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
        li { padding: 0.5rem 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding-left: 1rem; margin: 0.25rem 0; background: #eff6ff; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; }
        .status { display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
        .success { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
        .info { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🇺🇸 US States REST API</h1>
    <p><strong>API Base:</strong> <code>/states/</code> | <strong>Project:</strong> <span class="status info">Glitch Ready</span></p>
    
    <div class="endpoint">
        <h2>📋 GET Endpoints</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><code>GET /states/</code> <span class="status success">All 50 states + funfacts</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/?contig=true</code> <span class="status success">48 contiguous states</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/?contig=false</code> <span class="status success">AK + HI only</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/KS</code> <span class="status success">Full KS data + funfacts</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/KS/funfact</code> <span class="status success">Random KS fun fact</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/KS/capital</code> <span class="status success">{state, capital}</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/KS/nickname</code> <span class="status success">{state, nickname}</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/KS/population</code> <span class="status success">{state, population}</span></li>
            <li><code>GET /states/KS/admission</code> <span class="status success">{state, admitted}</span></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="endpoint">
        <h2>🔄 CRUD Fun Facts (MongoDB)</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><code>POST /states/KS/funfact</code> <span class="status info">{"funfacts": ["New fact 1", "New fact 2"]}</span></li>
            <li><code>PATCH /states/KS/funfact</code> <span class="status info">{"index": 1, "funfact": "Updated fact"}</span></li>
            <li><code>DELETE /states/KS/funfact</code> <span class="status info">{"index": 1}</span></li>
        </ul>
        <small><strong>Note:</strong> Index is 1-based. POST appends to existing facts.</small>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1rem; background: #fef3c7; border-radius: 8px;">
        <strong>✅ Pre-loaded fun facts:</strong> KS, MO, OK, NE, CO (3+ each)
    </div>
</body>
</html>